's entirely seperate from whether the enchanter class is properly tuned for gear appropriate content. I submit that it is not, but that you don't really have a way to discern this.<br></div><blockquote><div><span><br></span><hr size="2" width="100%"><span>And once a direction is given, it is pretty hard to 1. satisfy everyone, 2. move back to the previous state if it went too far.<br></span><hr size="2" width="100%"></div></blockquote><div>While I agree it's difficult to satisfy everyone completely, I think that there are some changes that would hit nearly all courts. Additionally, as shown by the tuning of ranger buffs not all that long ago, Sony has -no- problems yanking a change if they decide it made us too good. It's only when the changes make us too -bad- that it takes an act of god to get them to address it. =P<br></div></span><span><div><span></span><br><span></span></div><blockquote><div><span><br></span><br><br><span></span></div></blockquote></span><div></div>	
